Class Observation

java.lang.Object
org.ivoa.dm.proposal.prop.Observation
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.ivoa.vodml.jaxb.XmlIdManagement, org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulations, org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulationsForObjectType<Long>
Direct Known Subclasses:
CalibrationObservation, TargetObservation
@Entity @VoDml(id="proposal:Observation", role=objectType) public abstract class Observation extends Object implements org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulationsForObjectType<Long>, org.ivoa.vodml.jaxb.XmlIdManagement
An observation - a pointing of the telescope at a part of the sky, occurs in a single non-overlapping time period. objectType: Observation
